             were indicted for <rs id="t18190421-145-off793" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190421-145-off793" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-145-off793" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190421-145-cd794" type="crimeDate">1st of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-145-off793 t18190421-145-cd794"></join>, one pair of boots, value 3 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18190421-145-victim1504" type="victimName">
                     Charles James 
                     Bradley
                  <interp inst="t18190421-145-victim1504" type="surname" value="Bradley"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-145-victim1504" type="given" value="Charles James"></interp>
